data.description: Welcome Home!  This 3 bedroom/2.5 bath Sylvania Township is ready for you!  Kitchen boasts of granite counter tops! Relax and unwind on your new deck or sit around the fire pit when its a bit chilly out!  A new Erie metal roof will offer you peace of mind!  AC/Furnace replaced in 2020 and the HWT in 2018.  Laundry on the first floor and a spacious garage! Schedule your showing today!!
